# =============================================================================
# MR5 School — Monorepo environment index
# =============================================================================
# This repository has two deployable apps. Copy the matching example file in each
# project folder to `.env` (API) or `.env.local` (frontend).
#
#   client-main/.env.local.example     → client-main/.env.local
#   Mr5-School-API-main/.env.local.example → Mr5-School-API-main/.env
#
# See ENV_AUDIT_REPORT.md for the full variable inventory.
# =============================================================================
